{"tid":2492380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国山西化工廠爆炸現磨菇雲   2死3失蹤","createTime":"2021-04-17T05:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T05:45:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6d11a28aec1cdeb66cb692c2ab532a3590e65a7e","tid":2492380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/5d7f19107fb084ec79b46b453debd83b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210417/_2021041713050927045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F5d7f19107fb084ec79b46b453debd83b%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210417%2F_2021041713050927045.jpg&h=3c97713d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山西太原市興安化工廠一間工房發生爆炸，造成2人死亡，3人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸發生在今晨約8時半，消防接報後，當局立即啟動應急預案，成立應急救援小組，展開救援工作。經初步核查，有2人在事故中不幸遇難，3人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n事故處置工作還在進行當中，善後工作已經同步展開，事故原因正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline. com/news/realtime/chi/2049279</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2322208a24e6db59098a08c074407579c49c819a","tid":2492380,"uid":77717,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22c8793f3e4e193d834b89ab421a88793e1e0bd","tid":2492380,"uid":32221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"炸成咁先5個人受影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef98040bbfbe6573484a8a8cb3bc579afa7bc06","tid":2492380,"uid":214309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"上次唔係炸過一次咩 係咪舊文黎"},{"pid":"9e92e859b00b91f4c83087d4aecfe2e46c67ab70","tid":2492380,"uid":258967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"咁細配唔到樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj